'''Stormfront Studios''' was a North American video game developer. It developed [[The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers (video game)|''The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers'' (video game)]]. As of [[1 April|April 1]], [[2008]], the company is no longer doing business.
